* [[Yusuf Estes]], in {{cite news | publisher=Advance, [[University of Connecticut]] |date=۱۱-۱۷-۲۰۰۳ | title=Ramadan Awareness Event Designed To Debunk Negative Images | author=Elizabeth Omara-Otunnu | url=http://advance.uconn.edu/2003/031117/03111715.htm}}</ref> [[Montgomery Watt]], Norman Daniel, and [[Edward Said]] dismiss many of the criticisms as the product of old myths and medieval European polemics.<ref>
